        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Spell List</strong> occult</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Occultism, Performance</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Detect Magic]</em>; 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Ill Omen]</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Augury]</em>; 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wanderer's Guide]</em>; 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Suggestion]</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shadow Siphon]</em>; 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Truesight]</em>; 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Retrocognition]</em>; 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Unrelenting Observation]</em>; 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Weird]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Unraveling Blast]</em>; advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Invoke the Harrow]</em>; greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Rewrite Possibility]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> You become enveloped in possibility, represented as multiple versions of yourself from your possible futures overlaid on each other. You gain @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed]{Concealement} for 1 round, but can't use the concealment to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Hide].</p>"
